name: Space Tunnel
overview: Flee earthy mud and transcend it: choose the sky and take to space in one of those incredibly fast, strategically perfect and super versatile space ships. It is to be hoped that you have quite a bit of skill, because before you reach the promised land, you will have to squeeze through 7 space tunnels. And do not sit back and quietly nibble on some spacewokkels, because if you do not move, your time will expire. And do not forget your balancing exercises!
